### Generate deskripsi produk
POST http://localhost:5000/descriptions/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_name": "Sepatu Lari Nike Air Zoom",
  "features": ["Ringan", "Sol karet tebal", "Breathable mesh", "Ukuran 36-44"],
  "platform": "Tokopedia",
  "tone": "persuasif"
}

###

### Ambil semua deskripsi
GET http://localhost:5000/descriptions

###

### Ambil dengan pagination
GET http://localhost:5000/descriptions?page=1&per_page=5

###

### Hapus deskripsi berdasarkan ID
DELETE http://localhost:5000/descriptions/1

###
